data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Toss all those uncertain files into Scomp! Scomp will recursively search all directories within a given path. The program will pit all files against each other in a SHA-256 hash showdown. If they're identical, their color will change according to its uniqueness. If they're unique, their color will be disimilar to those that met the identical criteria. Upon completion, a listview will reveal all entities, color-coded to track their similarities!
